7 inch CM4 Products Comparision 
===============================

Chipsee provides two 7 inch Industrial Pi PCs, EPC/PPC-CM4-070 and PPC-CM4-070-D, here is the comparison:

.. table:: Comparison Between the 7 inch CM4 Products
   :align: center
   :width: 100%
   :class: align-center
   :widths: auto


   +-------------+---------------------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   | **Product** | **EPC/PPC-CM4-070**       | **PPC-CM4-070-D**                                                                                   |
   +=============+===========================+=====================================================================================================+
   | LAN         | 1 x LAN                   | 2 x LAN                                                                                             |
   +-------------+---------------------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   | USB-A       | 2 x USB 2.0               | 2 x USB 3.0                                                                                         |
   +-------------+---------------------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   | GPIO        | 8 x Optical Isolated GPIO | 6 x Raspberry Pi CPU GPIO (Compatible with Pi GPIO Software Libraries) or 8 x Optical Isolated GPIO |
   +-------------+---------------------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   | Connectors  | Distributed on each side  | Mostly on the bottom side                                                                           |
   +-------------+---------------------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   | Dimension   | 206 x 135 x 30mm          | 188.05 x 123.11 x 33.20mm, new case, small and compact                                              |
   +-------------+---------------------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
